steps.name: I navigate to my dashboard
I click on MFS fund transfer
I click on One Time Pay to Transfer Money via MFS "Rocket"

I select From Account Number "ACCOUNT - 0027-0250001161 / CONVENTIONAL", input To Account Number "016890865684" for "Rocket", transfer amount "50" below my available balance and remarks and confirm next to continue
I can see transaction details screen for "Rocket", select OTP channel, accept the terms and confirm next to continue by OTP verification
I can see transaction confirmation screen for "Rocket" transfer with success or fail status and the details of the transactions
I can download the transaction receipt for "Rocket" transfer
I can add the "Rocket" transfer transaction to favourite "RocketFav"
I can navigate to home clicking Go To Home for "Rocket" transfer
I click on MFS fund transfer
I click on One Time Pay to Transfer Money via MFS "Tap"
